# Network Traffic Analysis & Optimization Templates

This directory contains configuration templates for network monitoring and optimization tools.

## Available Templates

### netdata.conf
Netdata configuration for comprehensive network monitoring.

### tc-qos.conf
Traffic control (tc) QoS configuration templates.

### sysctl-tuning.conf
Kernel sysctl tuning parameters for network optimization.

### ntopng.conf
ntopng configuration for deep packet inspection.

## Usage

Copy templates to their respective locations and customize for your environment:

```bash
# Netdata configuration
cp templates/netdata.conf /etc/netdata/netdata.conf

# Traffic control
cp templates/tc-qos.conf /etc/tc/qos.conf

# Sysctl tuning
cp templates/sysctl-tuning.conf /etc/sysctl.d/99-network-tuning.conf

# ntopng configuration
cp templates/ntopng.conf /etc/ntopng/ntopng.conf
```
